{"about_the_game":"<strong>Screenshots are of a work-in-progress.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Ask, learn, and fight!</h2>Talk to people, read signs, and find other ways to learn about the world.<br><br>Use knowledge you gain to talk to people giving access to new understanding, new places, and new techniques.<br>Fight using the things that you learn on your adventure to reach new heights!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your group's escape begins with deciding who stays behind!</h2>Choose your own unique band of refugees giving each playthrough a different experience.<br><br>At the start of your journey your group's homeland is being attacked by a legendary beast!<br>You must divide the town into a party of refugees and a party to fight the attacker.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Seek help from Pinnacle for your homeland!</h2>Take the refugees on a journey to find help.<br><br>What your party learns and who comes along will change a lot about what's to come.<br>Will they reach Pinnacle?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Turn-based RPG combat with a unique twist.<br></li><li>Learn words and use them for advancing the plot, to find new things, and even in combat.<br></li><li>Create a unique party of 1 to 8 people of 9, leaving at least one behind!<br></li><li>A story of survival and personal growth.<br></li><li>A unique visual style that pops.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797570/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1724981279","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797570/page.bg.jpg?t=1724981279","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797570/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1724981279","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1797570/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1724981279","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptor